Text:
Nice one, ty!!!

Anyone happens to have their nature builder / gardening / biosphere collection add-ons???
Thanks a bunch! But say, i can't find install instructions or keygen anywhere, and i just instantly get requested to type in my seriel number on installation. What to do?
An install instruction would've been nice.

Hello,
I installed!
for anyone to install, proceed as follows:

1) Inside the install folder run the setup. Next enter the activation key:
7430B12A-3B67-4191-B0C5-59E57344CB1F
Do not open after installing the program! do not open!
2) In the patch folder, run the setup, and make install.
3) In the crack folder, run "MP4_EXPORT_FiX"
4) Within the "bin" folder, copy the "iClone"
5) Paste the file and replace "iClone" in the following location: C:  Program Files  Reallusion  iClone 5  bin
6) Inside the folder "CRACK  Content" copy the file "GUIResource.msx"
7) Cole and the file "GUIResource.msx" at the following location: C:  Program Files  Reallusion  iClone 5  Content
Activation was successful!

Leandro!
